    <ThingDef ParentName="GF40K_BaseRangedBoltRelic">
        <defName>GF40K_BoltPistolRelic</defName>
        <label>relic bolt pistol</label>
        <description>Bolt Pistol is a sidearm variant of a boltgun, commonly used by the Adeptus Astartes and other Imperial forces such as the Orders Militant of the Adepta Sororitas and certain members of the Astra Militarum and the Imperial Navy. As a Bolt Weapon, the Bolt Pistol is favoured over the Laspistol due to its improved killing ability, although it is less reliable and generally holds fewer shots in its magazine than a Laspistol - only 6 to 10 rounds of standard Bolter Ammunition, each weighing about 0.08 kilograms and with a diameter of .75 calibre (19.05 millimetres).\n\n This particular weapon was sanctified in one of the Ecclesiarchy temples, making it a holy relic of the Imperium. Still, this weapon is more than capable of bringing the Emperor's mercy to his foes.</description>
        <graphicData>
            <texPath>Things/Item/Equipment/WeaponRanged/Relic/BoltPistol_relic</texPath>
			<drawSize>1</drawSize>
        </graphicData>
        <soundInteract>Interact_Revolver</soundInteract>
